CSTutor.Model.Chat

Class Student

  • java.lang.Object
    • CSTutor.Model.Chat.Student

  • public class Student
extends java.lang.Object
    The student class houses all the information that the ChatWindow needs from students. It will house student ID, online status, and session ID.
